WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-GB

00:03:26.659 --> 00:03:27.659
10.
Visitors have chosen to scatter the ashes

00:03:27.659 --> 00:03:28.659
of loved ones in the rides, particularly inside
the Haunted Mansion.

00:03:28.659 --> 00:03:29.659
Employees have stated that they will simply
vacuum up any human remains left in the park.

00:03:29.659 --> 00:03:30.659
09.
In 2011 a costumed actor playing Donald Duck

00:03:30.659 --> 00:03:31.659
was accused of groping a female visitor to
the park.

00:03:31.659 --> 00:03:32.659
A Tigger actor also appeared in court after
being accused of fondling a 13-year-old but

00:03:32.659 --> 00:03:33.659
was declared innocent.

00:03:33.659 --> 00:03:34.659
08.
Original Pirates of the Caribbean ride props

00:03:34.659 --> 00:03:35.659
included real skeletons, as fakes were too
unrealistic.

00:03:35.659 --> 00:03:36.659
Borrowed from a medical center, the bodies
were eventually returned, except 1 skull which

00:03:36.659 --> 00:03:37.659
can still be seen.

00:03:37.659 --> 00:03:38.659
07.
In 2001 a 6-year-old lost a finger when it

00:03:38.659 --> 00:03:39.659
became caught in the trigger of a toy rifle
on Tom Sawyer Island.

00:03:39.659 --> 00:03:40.659
2 years later a 5-year-old lost half his foot
after it became stuck between the curb &amp; train

00:03:40.659 --> 00:03:41.659
tracks in the park.

00:03:41.659 --> 00:03:42.659
06.
In 2013 Disneyland was sued after a character

00:03:42.659 --> 00:03:43.659
dressed as the rabbit from Alice in Wonderland
was racist.

00:03:43.659 --> 00:03:44.659
He was seen posing only with white children,
physically turning his back on black visitors

00:03:44.659 --> 00:03:45.659
to the park.

00:03:45.659 --> 00:03:46.659
05.
Costumes for actors used to include communal

00:03:46.659 --> 00:03:47.659
underwear which was of often stained or smelly.
Staff reported outbreaks of pubic lice &amp; scabies

00:03:47.659 --> 00:03:48.659
before finally being given permission to wear
their own.

00:03:48.659 --> 00:03:49.659
4.
A quadriplegic with a life threatening spinal

00:03:49.659 --> 00:03:50.659
injury was abandoned in the It's A Small World
ride for 40 mins.

00:03:50.659 --> 00:03:51.659
Forced to listen to the song on repeat during
an evacuation, he was awarded $80k after suing

00:03:51.659 --> 00:03:52.659
for negligence.

00:03:52.659 --> 00:03:53.659
03.

00:03:53.659 --> 00:03:54.659
A 4-year-old suffered brain damage after getting
trapped beneath a 45lb Roger Rabbit 'taxicab'

00:03:54.659 --> 00:03:55.659
for 10 minutes.Unable to talk or walk, he
died 8 years after falling from the ride when

00:03:55.659 --> 00:03:56.659
staff failed to fully lower the lap bar.

00:03:56.659 --> 00:03:57.659
02.
In 1967 Disney was granted city status, earning

00:03:57.659 --> 00:03:58.659
the right to govern its own land.
As a result, they're entitled to build nuclear

00:03:58.659 --> 00:03:59.659
power plants on the site &amp; create a separate
criminal justice system.

00:03:59.659 --> 00:04:00.659
01.
A Disneyland Paris chef hung himself, leaving

00:04:00.659 --> 00:04:01.659
a note reading ""I don't want to work for
Mickey anymore"".

00:04:01.659 --> 00:04:02.659
Another employee poured petrol on himself.
He was stopped from setting himself alight

00:04:02.659 --> 00:04:02.662
by a colleague.

